# ============================================================================
# ‚úàÔ∏è FLIGHT TRACKING API - AviationStack (OPTIONAL)
# ============================================================================
# Get your free API key at: https://aviationstack.com/
# Free tier: 100 calls/month (sufficient for this trip)
# Used for: Live flight status, gate info, delay notifications
